    {
      "text": "The Disciples’ Grief Will Turn to Joy",
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "text": "Jesus went on to say,",
      "verse": 16,
      "type": "newline"
    },
    {
      "text": "At this, some of his disciples said to one another, “What does he mean by saying,  and ?”",
      "verse": 17,
      "type": "newline"
    },
    {
      "text": "They kept asking, “What does he mean by ? We don’t understand what he is saying.”",
      "verse": 18
    },
    {
      "text": "Jesus saw that they wanted to ask him about this, so he said to them,",
      "verse": 19,
